SPEC: Session expiration
  SUMMARY: Sessions expire after a period of inactivity.
  REQUIREMENT: Idle timeout
    The system SHALL expire authenticated sessions after 30 minutes.
    MARKS: test: code
    SCENARIO: Idle user
      WHENS:
        the user makes no requests for 30 minutes
      THENS:
        the next request returns 401
      MARKS: test: code
        crates/auth/tests/login.rs:42
        crates/auth/tests/integration.rs:117
